Implementations     |   // adds a student to the classList array
                    |   IS there space? (Space variable)
                    |   FOR LOOP
                    |   (ensures the amount of students doesn't exceed the max class space)
                    |       
                    |   IF space is equal to true, then insert the student
                    |   IF NOT then show there are not spaces available
                    | END METHOD
                    |   
                    | METHOD: void displayStudents
                    |   // displays all the students currently in the classList array
                    |   FOR LOOP
                    |       (Loop through the arrays indexes, printing them out to the screen)
                    |       (Also print what UNIT they are doing)
                    |   END FOR LOOP
                    | END METHOD
