                    | METHOD: void searchStudent
                    |   // displays a specific student
                    |   FOR LOOP
                    |       (loop through every person on the list)
                    |       IF a match is found
                    |           OUTPUT the details of the student
                    |       ELSE 
                    |           OUTPUT there was no student of that name
                    |       END ELSE IF
                    |   END FOR LOOP
                    | END METHOD
                    |   
                    | METHOD: void studentPass
                    |   // displays students who have passed the unit
                    |   FOR LOOP
                    |       (every student on the list)
                    |       IF a student has passed
                    |           OUTPUT the student HAS passed
                    |       ELSE 
                    |           OUTPUT the student HAS NOT passed
                    |       END ELSE IF
                    |   END FOR LOOP
                    | END METHOD: 
